ves JWT-authenticated HTTP requests, executes commands within a configurable workspace jail, manages files, and provides a health check endpoint.\n- **Scope:** Creates `pkg/picod/` package and `cmd/picod` entry point with server, auth, execute, and files sub-modules.\n- **Out of scope:** JWT key pair generation (Router's responsibility), public key injection (WorkloadManager's `injectPicodAuthEnv`), Docker image build, Helm charts.\n\n#### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/design.md`\n- **Status:** Mostly a skeleton template. Contains TODO placeholders throughout:\n  - Section 1.1 Purpose: `<!-- TODO: Describe the architectural purpose -->`\n  - Section 1.2 Package Layout: `├── TODO`\n  - Section 1.3 Dependencies: `| TODO | TODO | TODO |`\n  - Section 2 Data Model: `<!-- TODO: Define data structures -->`\n  - Section 3 Interfaces: `<!-- TODO: Define interfaces and method specifications -->`\n  - Section 4 Error Handling: `<!-- TODO: Define error types and handling matrix -->`\n  - Section 5.1 Unit Test Matrix: `<!-- TODO: Define test cases -->`\n  - Section 6 Deployment: `<!-- TODO: Deployment notes -->`\n  - Section 7 Implementation: `### Phase 1: TODO`\n  - Section 8 Future Changes: `<!-- TODO: Future work and known limitations -->`\n- **Only completed section:** Section 5.2 Gate Requirements (build/test/race/log checks)\n\n#### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md`\n- **Status:** 13 task groups (T1-T13) with **ALL checkboxes unchecked** (`[ ]`). This includes:\n  - T1: Define types and constants\n  - T2: Config and CLI flag parsing\n  - T3: AuthManager (JWT middleware and key loading)\n  - T4: Server struct, constructor, route registration\n  - T5: Health Check endpoint\n  - T6: Path sanitization (sanitizePath)\n  - T7: Command execution (ExecuteHandler)\n  - T8: File upload (UploadFileHandler)\n  - T9: File listing