 - ExecuteHandler with timeout, working_dir, env support |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/files.go` | 339 | Complete - sanitizePath, UploadFileHandler, ListFilesHandler, DownloadFileHandler, parseFileMode |\n\n---\n\n### 3. ENTRY POINT\n\n| File | Lines | Status |\n|------|-------|--------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/picod/main.go` | 15 | Complete - klog.InitFlags, ParseFlags, NewServer, Run |\n\n---\n\n### 4. TEST FILES IN `pkg/picod/`\n\n| File | Lines | Coverage |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/auth_test.go` | 247 | 8 tests: key loading (valid/missing/invalid-PEM), middleware (missing header, malformed, valid, expired, non-RSA, body size) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/config_test.go` | 54 | 4 tests: defaults, custom values, empty workspace->CWD, non-empty workspace->absolute |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/server_test.go` | 102 | 5 tests: field initialization, startTime, health public, API requires auth, all routes registered |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/health_test.go` | 74 | 3 tests: response fields, uptime increases, no auth required |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/execute_test.go` | 255 | 12 tests: valid execution, custom timeout, timeout exceeded, invalid timeout, empty command, malformed JSON, non-zero exit, working directory, invalid working dir, env augmentation, constant values |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/sanitize_test.go` | 121 | 9 tests: simple relative, traversal blocked, absolute stripped, symlink allowed, symlink escape blocked, non-existent allowed, empty workspace, workspace with symlinks, dotdot alone, dotdot with separator |\n\n---\n\n### 5. MISSING FILES (per tasks.md requirements)\n\n| Expected File | Task Reference | Status |\n|---------------|---------------|--------|\n| `pkg/picod/files_test.go` | T8, T9, T10 | **MISSING** - No test file for files.go (upload, list, download handlers) |\n| `pkg/picod/integration_test.go` | T12 | **MISSING** - No integration test file |\n\n---\n\n### 6. NO TODO/FIXME/DEFERRED MARKERS IN SOURCE CODE\n\nA search for `TODO|FIXME|DEFER|deferred|WIP|HACK|XXX` across all `.go` files in `pkg/picod/` returned **zero results**. The implementation code is clean of deferred-work markers.\n\n---\n\n### 7. CROSS-REFERENCES IN OTHER MODULES\n\n**AuthModePicoD constant** defined in:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` (line 13): `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"`\n\n**injectPicodAuthEnv** implemented in:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go` (line 567): Reads `picod-router-identity` Secret and injects `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` env var when `AuthMode == picod`\n\n**picod-router-identity Secret** used by:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/router/jwt.go` (line 25): `IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"` - Router generates/stores RSA key pairs\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go` (line 53): Same constant for WorkloadManager\n\n**Router JWT proposal** (AR-011) at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md`:\n- States \"PicoD 端的认证逻辑变更（已有完整实现，无需修改）\" - PicoD auth is already fully implemented, no changes needed.\n- Router and PicoD share the same key pair (Router stores, PicoD receives public key via env var).\n\n---\n\n### 8. STATUS SUMMARY: COMPLETED vs DEFERRED/INCOMPLETE\n\n| Aspect | Status | Details |\n|--------|--------|---------|\n| **Proposal document** | WRITTEN | Complete proposal.md with all sections |\n| **Design document** | INCOMPLETE | Skeleton with 8 TODO placeholders |\n| **Tasks checklist** | NOT CHECKED | All 13 task groups and 20 acceptance criteria have unchecked boxes |\n| **Delta spec** | COMPLETE | 490 lines of detailed Gherkin scenarios |\n| **Source code (pkg/picod/)** | IMPLEMENTED | All 6 .go files present with full implementations |\n| **Entry point (cmd/picod/)** | IMPLEMENTED | main.go present and complete |\n| **Test files** | PARTIALLY COMPLETE | 6 of 8 expected test files present |\n| **files_test.go** | **MISSING** | No tests for UploadFileHandler, ListFilesHandler, DownloadFileHandler, parseFileMode |\n| **integration_test.go** | **MISSING** | No end-to-end integration tests |\n| **TODO markers in source** | NONE | Clean code, no deferred work markers |\n| **Upstream deps (Router JWT, WorkloadManager injectPicodAuthEnv, AuthModePicoD)** | IMPLEMENTED | All referenced upstream components exist in the codebase |\n\n---\n\n### 9. KEY FINDINGS\n\n1. **The implementation code is complete but the tracking documents are out of sync.** All source files and most test files exist and appear fully implemented, yet the tasks.md checklist shows every single task as unchecked.\n\n2. **Two test files are genuinely missing:** `files_test.go` and `integration_test.go`. These correspond to tasks T8-T10 (file handlers) and T12 (integration tests) in the tasks checklist.\n\n3. **The design.md is a bare template** with no content filled in beyond the gate requirements section.\n\n4. **No deferred work markers** exist in the source code itself -- the implementation appears intentional and complete for the files that exist.\n\n5. **PicoD is deeply integrated** into the broader AgentCube architecture: the Router component signs JWTs using a shared RSA key pair stored in `picod-router-identity` Secret, the WorkloadManager injects the public key into sandbox pods via `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` environment variable, and the `AuthModePicoD` constant is defined in the shared API types.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_287a3bd25ffe2k9aD95IatpbDh","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore AR-015 PicoD API","time":{"start":1775840805591,"end":1775840975771}}}}
